column1: At first, I was really impressed with this knife. It was sharp and handled well, but after just a couple of weeks, the blade started to dull quickly. Even worse, the handle feels cheap and started to crack after washing it a few times. For the price, I expected better durability and performance. If you’re looking for a long-lasting knife, you might want to consider other options.
